On Tuesday two cub leaders came to our school one named Susie and the other named Christine, Susie is called a {Grey Beaver}.The Beavers are aged 5 to 7 and they are taught things they need to know before they go to Cubs.In the past they have had observation tests in the village and in the hall they have done tests with their senses of smell, sound, sight and taste. The Beavers often go on trails over to the park and study things about nature. They have a lot of fun.
{Christine.}
Christine is the leader of the {Wolf Pack}.At cubs she is called Arkela. You come to cubs after Beavers if you are between 7 to 10 you can join.They teach you things before you go to scouts.
